Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.72,0:00:06.14,default01,,0,0,0,,{\be2}So, you like tennis, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.43,0:00:08.14,default01,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.14,0:00:09.68,default01,,0,0,0,,{\be2}It's quite thrilling!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.89,0:00:11.56,default01,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Thrilling, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.56,0:00:13.02,default01,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Lucky you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.02,0:00:15.86,default01,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Well, you can expect a greater thrill soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.43,0:00:17.08,default01,,0,0,0,,{\be2}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.65,0:00:22.53,default01,,0,0,0,,{\be2}A person is about to be murdered...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.53,0:00:24.49,default01,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Somewhere in London...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.03,0:00:27.62,default01,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Right before your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:31.00,default01,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Tell Scotland Yard...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.96,0:00:33.87,default01,,0,0,0,,{\be2}It's my Revelation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.08,0:00:37.09,default01,,0,0,0,,{\be2}If it doesn't make sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.34,0:00:39.67,default01,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Go to Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:42.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the deciding moment that determines your future...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.05,0:00:44.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You cannot lie to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.38,0:00:47.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Edogawa Conan is being cornered...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.12,0:00:48.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Ran finds out, everything is doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.18,0:00:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.81,0:00:52.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.77,0:00:54.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.64,0:02:41.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After being invited by Diana{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, a British woman\Nwe happened to make the acquaintance of...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.06,0:02:43.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found ourselves preparing for a trip to London.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.17,0:02:47.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, since I can't fly overseas as Edogawa Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.22,0:02:52.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I temporarily returned to Kudou Shinichi's form\Nby taking medicine developed by Haibara...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:55.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And arrived at London separately from Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.27,0:03:00.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the Sherlock Holmes mecca of my dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:03.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So many places to go, I almost couldn't decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.86,0:03:09.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, what awaited us there was a premonition of a major case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:15.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apollo, younger brother of the famous tennis player Minerva Glass...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:18.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Received a letter from a suspicious man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.25,0:03:22.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Along with the words: "Someone will\Nbe murdered right before your eyes."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:29.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Written on the letter were sentences resembling ciphers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:34.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I was awakened by the loud sound of a rolling bell."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.68,0:03:37.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I am a long-nosed wizard in a castle."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.64,0:03:42.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"My morsel is a boiled egg that's gone as cold as a corpse."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:46.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'll finish up my meal by gnawing on a whole pickle."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.57,0:03:50.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Now I remember, I should order a celebratory cake in advance."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.03,0:03:54.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The sound of the bell stirs up my hatred."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.66,0:04:00.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"It tells me to finish everything by piercing\Nthe white back with two swords."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:04.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What on earth did this man want to express?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.09,0:04:10.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Per Apollo's request, we delivered the\Ncoded letter to Scotland Yard, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:15.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We learned there that many other children\Nhad also received the same coded letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:20.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If people are to die in front of these many children...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:24.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could this be a code indicative of a mass murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:41.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The British Museum!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:48.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Buckingham place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hyde Park...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:04:56.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:05:01.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've gone and checked out places where\Npeople would normally aggregate, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:03.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was nothing strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:06.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there wasn't anyone handing out strange flyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.94,0:05:10.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, since we got to sightsee London, it's not that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:11.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.15,0:05:15.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Being on the lookout for suspicious-looking\Npeople almost made me paranoid...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:17.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't relax and sightsee at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:18.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.41,0:05:22.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go buy some drinksâ€”wait for me around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.37,0:05:23.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:28.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A code, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:31.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I took a photo of it on my phone just in case, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.05,0:05:35.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all Greek to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:39.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if it were Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:42.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to call and ask him about this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.43,0:05:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It feels awkward...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:47.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.31,0:05:48.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stupid Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.48,0:05:51.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I yelled and hung up on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.03,0:05:53.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.57,0:05:56.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess he had reason to be displeased about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:06:03.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must've felt it as if I were bragging to him about\Nbeing at the place he'd wanted to go to for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.58,0:06:05.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was stupid of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.54,0:06:08.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was the one getting excited over nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:12.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd even gone so far as to look on the internet and take notes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.98,0:06:15.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.72,0:06:17.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.39,0:06:21.72,default01,,0,0,0,,Love hurts, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:29.69,default01,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.15,0:06:31.90,default01,,0,0,0,,Well, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:35.24,default01,,0,0,0,,Yes, something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.61,0:06:38.41,default01,,0,0,0,,You can't ask him for advice, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:42.87,default01,,0,0,0,,He's not an expert in that field, I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:45.41,default01,,0,0,0,,Who is "he"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:46.37,default01,,0,0,0,,Him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:47.25,default01,,0,0,0,,Up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.75,0:06:53.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sherlock Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.67,0:06:55.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:07:00.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had returned to Baker Street without even realizing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:03.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:05.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:06.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.35,0:07:09.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How nostalgic, the Japanese language.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.23,0:07:12.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I used to live in Japan, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:16.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My mother underwent eye surgery in Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:18.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And was hospitalized there for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:21.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.41,0:07:22.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Might you be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:24.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Minerva Glass{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:26.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The tennis player?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.41,0:07:30.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If this turns into a big deal, I won't be able to come here anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:39.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you come here often?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.51,0:07:40.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:43.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I always come here without fail before the Wimbledon finals...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.68,0:07:48.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to draw on Holmes's powers of\Nobservation and discernment to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.10,0:07:50.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really like Holmes, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.31,0:07:53.92,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose my mum's influence was strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:57.80,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,My father was German, but my mother English.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:57.41,Signs,,0,0,0,,Minerva Glass (22)\NTennis Player
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:08:00.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's a Sherlockian through and through.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:06.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But my mum has lost her vision, and can only\Nread Conan Doyle's works via Braille now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:11.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And my father and little sister who\Nwas six years younger than I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:13.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both passed away eight years ago in a traffic accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.29,0:08:16.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Minerva!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:21.72,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,When my father died, Apollo there was still in my mother's tummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:21.72,Signs,,0,0,0,,Apollo Glass (8)\NMinerva's Younger Brother
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:25.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm the central pillar of the Glass family today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.26,0:08:31.27,default01,,0,0,0,,I thought he was still around here, because he hadn't called...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.27,0:08:32.39,default01,,0,0,0,,But he isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:34.90,default01,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:38.44,default01,,0,0,0,,He's really an apprentice of Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:40.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:43.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:46.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That I was having love troubles...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:52.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because that face you had...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:56.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had seen myself with the same face in the mirror before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:09:00.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you've also had love troubles?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.09,0:09:03.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, I'm no longer troubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:05.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Holmes said it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.18,0:09:09.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Love is an emotional thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:12.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I will say nothing in praise of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:15.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"It is antagonistic to clear reasoning."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:18.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the same in tennis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:21.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love is 0.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.90,0:09:26.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how much you add to zero, you'll just lose miserably.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:35.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:37.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:40.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't it either!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:42.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.26,0:09:47.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There just isn't a place where two clock shops, a grocery store...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.89,0:09:52.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A cake shop, and a weapon shop are\Nconcentrated near a castle-like building!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.10,0:09:54.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:56.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's already 8:00 PM, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:09:59.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.19,0:10:00.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's still so bright out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:02.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.19,0:10:07.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time of year, it doesn't get dark in London until after 9:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.62,0:10:14.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran-neechan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.08,0:10:15.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:18.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "What's wrong?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.46,0:10:23.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you that we promised to have dinner with\NDiana{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} at 8:00 in the hotel restaurant, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:25.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:28.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so focused on solving the code with the professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.68,0:10:31.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're about to begin eating already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:34.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the professor and I will pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:37.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll just get fish and chips or something around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:38.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:40.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.36,0:10:42.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:46.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't there something like a landmark near you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:47.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.49,0:10:51.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a big ferris wheel next to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.24,0:10:52.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The London Eye, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:54.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we should get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:55.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Waiâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:58.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:04.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, the London Eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:06.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't we right next to Big Ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.38,0:11:09.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had no choice, did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:13.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she comes to pick us up, we'll have to\Nstop investigating this wicked cipher.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:16.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} will be worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:18.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.89,0:11:21.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll return to the hotel right about the time they finish their meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:26.28,default01,,0,0,0,,May I be excused?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:28.32,default01,,0,0,0,,I'll call my company.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:30.49,default01,,0,0,0,,Oh, you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:34.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just hold on, I'm gonna bring those two back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:37.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:43.84,default01,,0,0,0,,Now, can I ask about your successful adventures?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:46.76,default01,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sleeping Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:51.01,default01,,0,0,0,,What do you want me to speakingu now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:56.26,default01,,0,0,0,,As you can see, I've brought a party of friends tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.47,0:12:00.39,default01,,0,0,0,,Since I learned you're a famous defective in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:03.52,default01,,0,0,0,,Now, start your story, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.22,0:12:06.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O... OK...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:10.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The London Eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.24,0:12:12.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's really far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:16.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have a choice but to run there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.74,0:12:19.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not quite far enough to need a taxi for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.17,0:12:23.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, that Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.25,0:12:26.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Immersing himself in deductions to the\Npoint where he even forgets about hunger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:27.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:30.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.84,0:12:34.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Holmes said it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:38.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That the brain works best on an empty stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should call Shinichi and ask him about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.98,0:12:50.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like such an urgent cipher.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.90,0:12:52.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:54.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just can't bring myself to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:56.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.87,0:13:03.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It means that a large number of people\Nmight be killed at once, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.80,0:13:16.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems to me like this code may not be\Nindicating stores that sell certain things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.18,0:13:16.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.47,0:13:19.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first line goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:22.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I was awakened by the loud sound of a rolling bell."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:24.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:27.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I am a long-nosed wizard in a castle."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.65,0:13:33.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"My morsel is a boiled egg that's gone as cold as a corpse."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:38.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'll finish up my meal by gnawing on a whole pickle."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:44.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Now I remember, I should order a celebratory cake in advance."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.71,0:13:48.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The sound of the bell stirs up my hatred."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.34,0:13:51.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, the last...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:57.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"It tells me to finish everything by piercing\Nthe white back with two swords."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:14:00.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't make heads nor tails of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.68,0:14:04.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I could at least figure out what the "loud\Nsound of a rolling bell" in the first line meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.77,0:14:06.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'd have a clue to latch onto, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:12.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.07,0:14:15.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell her to let me concentrate on the code?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:17.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.74,0:14:19.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Shinichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.49,0:14:21.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.08,0:14:23.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.54,0:14:25.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Shinichi's phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.54,0:14:26.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're asleep, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:29.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know it's only 5:00 AM in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.38,0:14:32.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I've been awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.21,0:14:33.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.17,0:14:35.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:38.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have yelled at you and hung up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.05,0:14:44.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so excited to be in the place\Nwhere you had always wanted to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:46.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you must've thought I was just bragging.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:48.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It didn't really bother me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:51.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I really had things I was busy with at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.52,0:14:52.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:14:54.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:58.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Shinichi, there's a code I want you to solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:03.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that code, that Conan kid already forwarded it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:07.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I've been thinking about it without sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:10.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the beginning part, "the loud sound of a rolling bell"...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.92,0:15:13.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is where I'm stuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.67,0:15:16.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Loud sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:18.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rolling bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.12,0:15:44.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:45.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Big Ben, Big Ben!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:48.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You hear it, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:51.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Big Ben's chime here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.46,0:15:53.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what "loud sound of a rolling bell" was referring to!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.09,0:15:56.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Big Ben here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.01,0:16:00.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.26,0:16:01.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:02.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:04.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:05.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In London!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.35,0:16:06.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.39,0:16:11.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just happened to tune into a live broadcast from London on TV...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.44,0:16:13.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're here, aren't you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.15,0:16:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:16.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got another call coming in...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.90,0:16:17.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.28,0:16:23.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:27.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His weak reaction back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:30.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And his apparent annoyance when trying to hang up...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.58,0:16:34.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was all because he's here in London!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.05,0:16:42.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.13,0:16:42.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.51,0:16:44.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:47.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you trick her into thinking we're next to the London Eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:49.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the time being...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.06,0:16:52.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's flee!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:54.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.65,0:17:06.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's how I sent the culprit flying\Nwith my one-armed shoulder throw.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:07.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, baritsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.41,0:17:09.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Baritsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:11.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.37,0:17:11.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Judo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:13.54,default01,,0,0,0,,That's baritsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.54,0:17:16.96,default01,,0,0,0,,Which Holmes performed on Professor Moriarty when they fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:20.96,default01,,0,0,0,,Mastering baritsu means you're a brilliant detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:22.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No idea what she's saying, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:24.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:25.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:28.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strongu detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:34.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew something was fishy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:36.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To think Shinichi's not envious about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:39.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't let him have his way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.65,0:17:42.36,default01,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.49,0:17:48.12,default01,,0,0,0,,Have you seen a Japanese boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:49.78,default01,,0,0,0,,Yes, I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.95,0:17:53.75,default01,,0,0,0,,I do believe he was rushing to the bridge over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.12,0:17:56.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.25,0:17:57.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bridge I just crossed!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.25,0:18:00.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must've crossed from the opposite walkway...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:06.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\t(50,51,\fscy150\fscx150)}{\t(100,101,\fscy100\fscx100)}{\t(150,151,\fscy150\fscx150)}{\t(200,201,\fscy100\fscx100)}{\t(250,251,\fscy150\fscx150)}{\t(300,301,\fscy100\fscx100)}{\t(350,351,\fscy150\fscx150)}SHINICHI!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:10.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:12.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we don't manage to hide somewhere, she'll catch up to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.73,0:18:15.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two Japanese people together will stand out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:17.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's split up and flee after we get across the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.98,0:18:19.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.86,0:18:23.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.28,0:18:30.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This damn drain cover was open...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.37,0:18:34.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something written on the side of this drain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.21,0:18:37.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Valley of Fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.08,0:18:39.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Kyoufu no Tani."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:41.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the title of one of Holmes's stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:44.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.97,0:18:51.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would that be there...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.77,0:19:01.11,default01,,0,0,0,,Did you see a Japanese boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.77,0:19:03.27,default01,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:04.69,default01,,0,0,0,,I saw him running over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:09.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:11.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:14.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.45,0:19:17.83,default01,,0,0,0,,I just passed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.21,0:19:21.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.88,0:19:23.88,default01,,0,0,0,,Have you seen a Japanese boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.13,0:19:27.51,default01,,0,0,0,,Oh, the boy has...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.51,0:19:29.93,default01,,0,0,0,,Run into a phone booth just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:33.05,default01,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.47,0:19:34.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:40.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she finds me now, she'll know I'm Kudou Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.73,0:19:48.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:49.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:55.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:19:58.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't run away anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:01.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Explain to me what this is all about!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:04.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,SHINICHI!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:30.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Explain what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:33.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just happen to have come to London as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.03,0:20:35.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.91,0:20:38.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me he took the antidote meant for the return trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:43.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why were you running?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.54,0:20:45.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:49.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I forgot to tell you that I was coming to London...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.30,0:20:52.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I thought it'd be awkward...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.59,0:20:54.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.05,0:20:56.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You had plenty of{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ces to, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.81,0:20:59.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:00.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:02.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stupid of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:05.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got excited over nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:10.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did so much research, and was worried to death about your stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.57,0:21:13.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that stupid of me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:18.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just like that person said.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.20,0:21:20.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love is 0...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.16,0:21:24.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how much you add to zero, you'll just lose miserably.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:26.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.92,0:21:29.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Minerva Glass{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said so!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.09,0:21:31.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Minerva Glass?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.01,0:21:33.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You met the Grass Court Queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.55,0:21:35.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.68,0:21:36.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At Baker Street!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.39,0:21:38.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.43,0:21:39.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At Baker Street?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.18,0:21:42.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, was there a kid with her!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.06,0:21:44.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.48,0:21:46.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said he was her younger brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.81,0:21:49.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did that kid say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.44,0:21:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like if he came back because he remembered anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.82,0:21:55.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.49,0:21:57.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Calm down...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.70,0:21:59.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.79,0:22:02.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a detective, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.29,0:22:06.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you call yourself a detective, then why\Ndon't you try to deduce what's in my heart!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.71,0:22:07.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.14,0:22:11.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.09,0:22:11.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.80,0:22:14.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.48,0:22:19.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.66,0:24:03.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sender of the "Revelation" turned out\Nto be an extremely nefarious criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.41,0:24:06.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we don't solve the code soon, anything bad could happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.58,0:24:08.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.75,0:24:10.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Find some clues at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.81,0:24:32.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
